 	<li><span style="font-weight: 400;"> Â  Â  Vitamin A- rich foods like those that you get from orange and green coloured fruits and vegetables.</span></li>
 	<li><span style="font-weight: 400;"> Â  Â  Vitamin C-rich foods like peppers, peas, citrus fruits.</span></li>
 	<li><span style="font-weight: 400;"> Â  Â  Iron rich foods like dates, spinach, jaggery.Â </span></li>
