 	<li><span style="font-weight: 400;"> Â  Â  Cinnamon and Honey mixture could put up a good fight against swine flu.</span></li>
</ul>
<b>Treatments</b>

<span style="font-weight: 400;">Just like any other flu, H1N1 can be treated through antiviral medications like Tamiflu and Relenza. These medicines do not cure the illness but help in shortening the duration of symptoms or help in making the symptoms less severe.</span>

